{"tid":2451433,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"IQ 160 羅致光：放無薪假如分享工作","createTime":"2021-03-18T05:52:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-18T07:20:24.000Z","uid":7542,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"71dbf1931b4b7c585d11af119f87c6b29dfcdf86","tid":2451433,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T05:52:15.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>有冇 IQ 161 嘅解釋吓佢 up 乜</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n金融服務界張華峰關注，業界不少經紀及後勤員工須放無薪假，要求政府考慮推出新的支援措施。<br />\n<br />\n羅致光回應，<span class=\"red\"><strong>僱員放無薪假，某程度反映市場有變化，有如「Job Sharing（工作分享）」，反映市場靈活性。員工本來5天工作，變成4天工作，如果大家不分享工作，實際上僱主可解僱20%員工，甚至40%，希望僱主與僱員互諒互讓，即使放無薪假會影響僱員收入，但總比裁員好</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20210318/s00002/1616005944753/%e6%8e%a8%e7%ac%ac%e4%b8%89%e6%9c%9f%e4%bf%9d%e5%b0%b1%e6%a5%ad%e3%80%8c%e5%a5%bd%e6%9c%89%e4%bf%9d%e7%95%99%e3%80%8d-%e7%be%85%e8%87%b4%e5%85%89-%e6%94%be%e7%84%a1%e8%96%aa%e5%81%87%e5%a6%82%e5%88%86%e4%ba%ab%e5%b7%a5%e4%bd%9c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20210318%2Fs00002%2F1616005944753%2F%25e6%258e%25a8%25e7%25ac%25ac%25e4%25b8%2589%25e6%259c%259f%25e4%25bf%259d%25e5%25b0%25b1%25e6%25a5%25ad%25e3%2580%258c%25e5%25a5%25bd%25e6%259c%2589%25e4%25bf%259d%25e7%2595%2599%25e3%2580%258d-%25e7%25be%2585%25e8%2587%25b4%25e5%2585%2589-%25e6%2594%25be%25e7%2584%25a1%25e8%2596%25aa%25e5%2581%2587%25e5%25a6%2582%25e5%2588%2586%25e4%25ba%25ab%25e5%25b7%25a5%25e4%25bd%259c&d=1mBOIAkAA7%2FwaZBThmus2Z1e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=602e4412\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20210318%2Fs00002%2F1616005944753%2F%25e6%258e%25a8%25e7%25ac%25ac%25e4%25b8%2589%25e6%259c%259f%25e4%25bf%259d%25e5%25b0%25b1%25e6%25a5%25ad%25e3%2580%258c